Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Boss
    The Boss class represents the final enemy which the Hero can defeat with all of the same abilities as the Hero.
    DrawingSurface
    The surface that draws and runs the game
    Enemy
    The Enemy class represents the enemy which can move and cause damage to the Hero.
    Fireball
    The Fireball class represents a fire ball which is one of the projectiles that the Hero can collect.
    FireEnemy
    The FireEnemy class represents an Enemy with the Fireball projectile which the Player can defeat.
    GrassEnemy
    The GrassEnemy class represents an Enemy with the Leaf Dash move which the Player can defeat.
    Hero
    The Hero class represents the playable main character which can move and use special projectiles.
    Main
    Main class that runs the program
    MovingImage
    The MovingImage class represents an image which moves.
    Platform
    The Platform class represents a movable platform on which the Hero and enemies can stand.
    Projectile
    The Projectile class represents the different projectiles which the player can gain and the enemies have.
    Spike
    The Spike class represents a Spike which can cause damage to the Hero and Enemies if they walk into it.
    WaterEnemy
    The WaterEnemy class represents an Enemy with the Waterfall projectile which the Player can defeat.
    Waterfall
    The Waterfall class represents a water fall which is one of the abilities that the Hero can collect.
